implicit wait is only when element is present if not present like loading or something then it can not fetch it
Implicit wait only waits for element presence, not for:
visibility
text loading
so for this we use explicit wait


Wait Type	    Works For
Implicit Wait -	Element present in DOM
Explicit Wait -	Condition (visible, clickable, text present)

in implicit wait we do not give any condition but for explicit we give condition
implicit is applicable for all find_element but explicit will be applicable for that one element only

